Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:03.60,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{To sate her desire to make books,}Mình muốn làm sách,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.10,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{Main completed her clay tablets.}Myne đã làm bảng đất sét.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.70,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{But her attempt to fire them \Nended in another failure.}Nhưng cuối cùng thì thất bại.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:13.15,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{Then came summer...}Và mùa hè đã đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.30,Italics_top,F,0,0,0,,{And the day of Turi's baptism.}Cũng đến ngày rửa tội cho Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.62,Title,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1700,1)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}Sự thống trị của mọt sách
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:59.04,Title2,Title Card,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,500)}{Ascendance of a Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:09.98,Ep Title,Ep Title,0,0,0,,{Chapter Five\NBaptisms and Strange Fevers}Lễ rửa tội và cơn sốt kì lạ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.14,0:02:17.20,Default,Carla,0,0,0,,{My, Turi! You look adorable!}Ồ Turi! Cháu dễ thương quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.11,Default,W,0,0,0,,{Congratulations, Turi.}Chúc mừng Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.98,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:31.13,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{It is customary in this world to throw a \Ngrand celebration for seven-year-olds.}Khi trẻ lên 7 tuổi sẽ được tổ chức một buổi lễ hoành tráng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.54,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{The same day, they are \Nbaptized at the cathedral.}Và sẽ được rửa tội tại nhà thờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.18,Default,C,0,0,0,,{Must be nice to have girls.}Có con gái thật tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:43.29,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You do only have boys, Carla. \NRalph, Lutz, Sascha and Sieg.}Chị thì chỉ toàn con trai nhỉ.\N Ralph, Lutz, Sascha và Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.39,Default,C,0,0,0,,Thiệt tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.93,Default,C,0,0,0,,{It's so tiresome.}Chán thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.68,Default,C,0,0,0,,{Wow...}Ồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.07,Default,C,0,0,0,,{You even did your hair up so nicely.}Trang trí tóc đẹp quá nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.52,Default,C,0,0,0,,{You look like a princess, Turi!}Trong cháu như công chúa vậy, Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.66,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Main did it for me.}Myne làm cho cháu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:02:59.97,Default,C,0,0,0,,{What? Main did?}Hả? Myne á?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:03.03,Default,C,0,0,0,,{So she has more to her \Nthan her unusual recipes.}Không chỉ biết nấu ăn mà còn làm được mấy việc khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.74,Default,W,0,0,0,,{Hey, look. I've never seen a \Nhair ornament like this before.}Nhìn kìa, tôi chưa từng thấy đồ trang trí tóc nào thế này cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.87,Default,W,0,0,0,,{You're right. It's so pretty.}Phải nhỉ, đẹp quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.66,Default,W,0,0,0,,{How was it made?}Làm thế nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.50,Default,W,0,0,0,,{Wow! Amazing!}Tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:21.01,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{The hair ornament I made is that unusual?}Đồ trang trí mình làm đẹp đến thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.19,Default,G,0,0,0,,{No way!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to a meeting \Non such an important day!}Mình sẽ không đi họp vào ngày hôm nay đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Only the kids get to enter \Nthe cathedral, right?}Chỉ có con nít mới được vào nhà thờ mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:35.79,Default,G,0,0,0,,{It's a father's duty to wait at the \Ncathedral's plaza during baptism.}Trách nhiệm của người cha là chờ ngoài sảnh đến khi xong lễ rửa tội.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:40.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Isn't it also a father's duty to go \Nto work and provide for the family?}Con tưởng trách nhiệm của người \Ncha là đi làm kiếm tiền lo cho gia đình?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.11,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I know, I know.}Ba biết rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.91,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Let's go down Central Avenue!}Nào, đến Đại lộ Trung tâm thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:03:59.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.64,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Smile.}Cười lên nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:06.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{As long as you're smiling, you're \Nprettier than anybody else.}Chỉ cần cười thôi là chị sẽ đẹp nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Sheesh, Main. Don't lie to me.}Thiệt tình... Myne này...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.73,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Time to go!}Đi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad...}Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{We need to go.}Chúng ta đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:32.36,Default,G,0,0,0,,Turi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.66,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You won't make it for the meeting!}Ba định không đi họp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.04,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You're late, Captain!}Anh đến trễ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.68,Italics_top,O,0,0,0,,Đã bảo hôm nay họp rồi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.68,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I told you about the \Nmeeting today, didn't I?}Trong khi ba đi họp...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.91,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I was to practice writing.}Mình luyện viết chữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.71,Default,G,0,0,0,,Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto's in a meeting right now.}Chú Otto đang họp rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.80,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Hey, Main.}A, Myne à.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.29,Default,G,0,0,0,,{I forgot about that.}Chú quên mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.02,Default,G,0,0,0,,{What do I do now?}Làm sao giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.61,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Shall I read it for you?}Cháu đọc thay được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.53,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You can read?}Cháu có thể đọc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:05.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I know how to read identification papers \Nand introductory letters from nobility.}Nếu là giấy tờ tùy thân hay thư giới thiệu của quý tộc thì được ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto taught me.}Chú Otto đã dạy cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.56,Default,G,0,0,0,,{It's the latter.}Là thư giới thiệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.54,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Please.}Nhờ cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.40,Default,M,0,0,0,,{He has a referral from Baron Bron,}Ông ấy có thư giới thiệu từ Nam tước Bron,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,{and is going to visit Baron Graz.}và đến thăm Nam tước Graz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This needs the captain's stamp,}Cần đóng dấu từ Đội trưởng,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.35,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but he's in a meeting.}nhưng ba đang họp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Show him to the waiting \Nroom for lesser nobles.}Hãy dẫn ông ấy đến phòng chờ dành cho quý tộc cấp thấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A merchant with a noble's referral}Một thương nhân với thư giới thiệu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:37.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{should understand if we explain \Nthe situation to him.}thì sẽ hiểu nếu chúng ta giải thích tình hình.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.86,Default,G,0,0,0,,{We're going home, Main.}Chúng ta về thôi, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.06,Default,G,0,0,0,,{We're leaving before Otto catches us.}Chúng ta phải trốn trước khi bị Otto tóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wait, Dad!}Khoan đã ba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I need to report something to him!}Con cần báo lại vài chuyện với chú ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.95,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Main?}Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.33,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, Mister Otto!}A, chú Otto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:53.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A merchant with a noble's referral is here!}Một thương nhân có thư giới thiệu đang ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:57.07,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I've had him shown to the waiting \Nroom for lesser nobles,}Cháu đã để ông ấy trong phòng chờ dành cho quý tộc cấp thấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{so please see to him immediately!}Nên chú hãy đi gặp ông ấy đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.82,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Well done! That's my assistant!}Làm tốt lắm! Không hổ là trợ lý của chú!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.04,Default,G,0,0,0,,{My daughter, you mean!}Con gái tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Dad...}Ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.05,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:17.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Also, the cathedral was really \Nbeautiful and spacious!}Và nhà thơ rất to với tráng lệ nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:19.72,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Really? Good for you.}Thật hả? Tuyệt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Yep!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This is for you.}Cho chị nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.87,Default,T,0,0,0,,{What is this? So cute!}Gì thế? Dễ thương quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.74,Default,T,0,0,0,,{And so yummy!}Và ngon nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.66,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Those are some interesting shapes.}Hình dạng kì lạ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.37,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You may really have a \Ntalent for cooking, Main.}Con đúng là có tài nấu nướng đó, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thanks for making this.}Cảm ơn em nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.21,Default,T,0,0,0,,{And the hair ornament, too.}Cả cái đồ trang trí hôm nay nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.17,Default,T,0,0,0,,{I was really happy today.}Chị vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.63,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Turi is such an angel!}Thiên thần!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.02,Default,G,0,0,0,,{We have presents for you, Turi.}Bọn ta có quà cho con nè, Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.02,Default,E,0,0,0,,{They're work clothes and tools.}Là quần áo làm việc và công cụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.62,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Take good care of them.}Con hãy giữ cẩn thận nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:09.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Dad, Mom!}Cảm ơn ba mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Good luck being an apprentice seamstress.}Cố gắng học việc thật tốt nhé Turi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:18.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Will she have to go to work every day?}Chị ấy sẽ phải đi làm mỗi ngày ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.29,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Only for half the week at first.}Lúc đầu chỉ nửa tuần thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.97,Default,T,0,0,0,,{For the other half, I'll go \Nto the forest like always.}Nửa tuần còn lại thì vẫn vào rừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:28.34,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I see. Thank goodness.}Vậy à, may quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.91,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Main's baptism is coming up next year, too.}Năm sau là đến con đó Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:34.17,Default,T,0,0,0,,{Have you decided what to \Ndo for apprentice work?}Em đã chọn được nghề mình muốn làm chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:37.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I wanna run a bookstore.}Vâng, em sẽ mở hiệu sách.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,{A bookstore?}Hiệu sách?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:45.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Uh... I'd be selling books, \Nso a merchant, I guess?}Là nơi bán sách... Có thể gọi là thương nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.48,Default,G,0,0,0,,{Well, I don't really understand,}Ba không hiểu lắm,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.57,Default,G,0,0,0,,{but it's fine as long as you have a goal.}nhưng miễn con có mục tiêu là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.78,Default,G,0,0,0,,{That aside, this is for you.}Và cái này là cho con.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:08:00.17,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You'll be helping with housework \Nin Turi's place from now on.}Con sẽ thế chỗ Turi làm việc nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.16,Default,G,0,0,0,,{You'll need this to get firewood \Nand forage in the forest.}Con sẽ cần nó để kiếm củi và tìm thức ăn trong rừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,{A knife!}Dao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:11.37,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Can't I use this to make wood tablets?}Mình có thể dùng nó để tạo bản gỗ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:15.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll chop wood into thin strips,}Chặt gỗ thành thanh mỏng,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:19.09,Default,M,0,0,0,,{shave the surface to smooth them,}bào bề mặt cho nhẵn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,{and write on them.}và viết lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{All done!}Xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.06,wood,Sign,0,0,0,,{ABCDE}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.95,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If I make a lot, they'll be a \Nfine substitute for a book!}Nếu làm nhiều thì có thể tạo được một cuống sách!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.91,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Ancient China!}Cảm ơn nền văn minh Trung Quốc cổ đại!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yahoo!}Yà hú!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:45.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This knife... is too heavy!}Dao... nặng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Lutz and Turi are amazing.}Lutz và Turi tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I should start with what I can do, too.}Mình cũng nên bắt tay vào làm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Well, that's how it goes at first.}Đầu tiên ai chẳng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This could work!}Được đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.55,Default,L,0,0,0,,{What are you making now to \Nreplace the clay tablets?}Thay vì làm bản đất sét thì lần này cậu làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.28,Default,M,0,0,0,,Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How could you tell these were \Na clay tablet replacement?}Sao cậu biết tớ đang làm cái này thay bản đất sét?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.23,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I mean,}Thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.79,Default,L,0,0,0,,{you're having so much fun.}cậu đang rất vui mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Looked like you were about to rub \Nyour cheek against the wood.}Trông như cậu định cọ má mình vào nó vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:04.11,Default,L,0,0,0,,{You were also fascinated by \Nthe clay tablets, remember?}Lúc làm bản đất sét cậu cũng thế còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.39,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I had no idea! That's so embarrassing!}Xấu hổ quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.91,Default,L,0,0,0,,{So, what're you making?}Vậy cậu làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.30,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wood tablets.}Bản gỗ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.98,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Wood tablets?}Bản gỗ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.97,Default,L,0,0,0,,{You'll write on these this time?}Cậu sẽ viết lên nó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I need lots of these.}Ừm, tớ cần nhiều hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.64,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Okay, I get it. I'll help you.}Hiểu rồi, tớ sẽ giúp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:25.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.61,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Yeah! But in return...}Ờ, đổi lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:34.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Can you introduce me to this Otto person?}Cậu giới thiệu tớ với chú Otto được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto?}Chú Otto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I wanna ask him about the traveling trade.}Tớ muốn hỏi chú ấy về thương nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:44.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll ask when I go to the gate tomorrow.}Ngày mai tớ sẽ hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But he's a busy man.}Nhưng chú ấy bận lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:49.03,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sorry in advance if he refuses.}Nếu bị từ chối thì xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.76,Default,L,0,0,0,,{That's fine.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.49,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Main!}Cảm ơn Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto.}Chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.86,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How does one join the traveling trade?}Muốn đi du hành thì cần những gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:09.71,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Huh? You want to be a traveling trader?}Hả? Cháu muốn làm thương nhân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.98,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Wait, is this my fault?}Không lẽ là tại chú?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.16,Default,O,0,0,0,,{The captain's gonna kill me!}Đội trưởng giết chú mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, no! My friend does, not me!}À không, là bạn cháu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.96,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Oh...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.02,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Then you should tell them not to bother.}Thế thì cháu nên bảo bạn là bỏ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ah, I knew it.}À, quả nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.86,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You know what?}Là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:32.49,Default,M,0,0,0,,{From the way he spoke, I figured \Nit wasn't a popular profession.}Nghe cậu ấy bảo thì đó không phải một nghề phổ biến.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:36.08,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Well, he'd probably catch \Nhell from his parents.}Ừm, để ba mẹ phát hiện là chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:40.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Also, I thought that a \Nlife of constant travel}Và cháu nghĩ một cuộc sống đi khắp nơi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,{would be too hard on a city kid.}hẳn phải rất khó cho một đứa trẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.47,Default,O,0,0,0,,{If you know that much, why not \Ngive him your own advice?}Nếu rành thế thì sao cháu không khuyên bạn mình đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Rather than a city kid like me,}Thay vì nghe lời một đứa nhóc thành phố như cháu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:55.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{he'd probably listen if you \Ngave him a dose of reality.}thì nghe từ người từng trải như chú thuyết phục hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.85,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Hmm...}Ừm..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.70,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You have ties with merchants, don't you?}Chú vẫn còn liên kết với những thương nhân ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,{If he looks to become a merchant,}Nếu cậu ấy muốn trở thành thương nhân,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,{he can leave the town at \Ntimes to stock up on goods.}thì có thể rời khỏi nơi này để buôn bán hàng hóa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.82,Default,O,0,0,0,,{If you're acting as a go-between,}Cháu có vẻ nói nhiều về người bạn này,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.07,Default,O,0,0,0,,{you must like that kid a lot.}quan tấm đến bạn đó vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.75,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Lutz has helped me loads.}Lutz lúc nào cũng giúp cháu cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.41,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I want to repay him when I can.}Nên muốn trả ơn cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.56,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I see. Hmm...}Vậy à... Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.18,Default,O,0,0,0,,{The next day off should be fine.}Lần nghỉ tiếp theo được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Mister Otto!}Cảm ơn chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.82,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.25,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{How do I write on the wood tablets?}Mình viết lên bản gỗ bằng gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.51,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Slate pencils won't work.}Đá viết bảng không được rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:38.01,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto, can I be paid in \Nink instead of slate pencils?}Chú Otto, cháu có thể được trả bằng mực thay vì đá không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.77,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You'd have to work three \Nyears for free. No advances.}Cháu sẽ phải dùng nó 3 năm. Không có ưu đãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.95,Eyecatch_an4,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.08,Eyecatch_an6,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1)}{Ascendance of a\N Bookworm}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:02.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mister Otto said he can see \Nyou on his next day off.}Chú Otto nói lần nghỉ sau có thể gặp nhau đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.54,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.55,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Main!}Cảm ơn Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:11.15,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I hope it proves to be \Na good meeting for you.}Hi vọng là một cuộc gặp tốt đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:19.15,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now I just dry them.}Giờ chỉ cần chờ khô.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.61,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Next up is...}Tiếp theo là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ink. Ink?}Mực... Mực...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Should I go catch an octopus \Nor a squid or something?}Bắt mực hay bạch tuộc để lấy mực à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.66,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Now I can write!}Giờ thì có thể viết được!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Not! Where's the sea even supposed to be?!}Khoan! Mà biển ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.72,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ash?}Tro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.63,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Ash could work!}Có thể được!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom!}Mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Can I have that ash?}Cho con đống tro đó nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.05,Default,E,0,0,0,,{No. It's used to make soap,}Không, tro dùng để làm xà phòng,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:57.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,{thaw ice, and do all kinds of things.}làm tan băng và nhiều việc khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.36,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How about soot, then?}Thế còn bồ hóng?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.27,Default,E,0,0,0,,{My! You'll clean the oven for me?!}Con dọn giùm mẹ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.46,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Good luck, Main.}Cảm ơn con, Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{So yeah, I did my best.}Tớ đã cố gắng lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.41,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I was bedridden after that, though.}Sau đó thì nằm liệt giường.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.11,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Bedridden again?}Lại bệnh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.62,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?}Ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.47,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm fine now.}Ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:24.68,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Anyway, let's try using this soot to write.}Mà thử viết chữ xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Guess I'll try mixing it in water first.}Đầu tiên trộng với nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.18,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The soot and water will probably separate.}Nước và bồ hóng không tan vào nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.42,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Why not try writing with it?}Viết thử xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.07,Default,L,0,0,0,,{It's getting fuzzy.}Nó nhòe kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{This won't work.}Thất bại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.27,Default,L,0,0,0,,{What next?}Tiếp theo là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:51.73,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I think mixing it with oil \Nis the obvious choice, but...}Tớ định trộn với dầu nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,{No way you can get oil.}Dầu khó kiếm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.50,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom won't let me have any.}Mẹ cũng chẳng cho tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What else?}Còn gì không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.96,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It doesn't have to be a liquid. If I can \Nmake something like a crayon or pencil...}Không cần phải là chất lỏng... \NNếu có thể làm được bút chì hay bút màu thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's it!}Chính là nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.52,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Let's try mixing it with clay.}Thử trộn với đất sét xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.28,Default,Bo,0,0,0,,{All right!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:32.92,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Done!}Xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.88,Default,M,0,0,0,,{How long should we let these dry?}Phải để khô tầm bao lâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.35,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Beats me.}Không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Wanna try firing them?}Nướng nó thử xem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:46.35,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Don't try anything stupid.\NDo you want another explosion?}Đừng làm chuyện ngu ngốc. Cậu quên vụ nổ rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.42,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Urk.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:52.51,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I can write on \Nwood tablets with this.}Nhưng tớ có thể viết lên bản gỗ bằng thứ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.29,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I've taken a step toward \Nmy book-making goal.}Vậy là tiến gần một bước đến việc làm sách rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'll dry these in storage, too.}Mình sẽ mang nó phơi trong kho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.11,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Huh? They're gone!}Ủa? Đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.14,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:09.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Main?}Sao thế Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:12.81,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom! Do you know where the \Nwood tablets here went?}Mẹ! Mẹ có thấy bản gỗ của con đâu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Wood tablets?}Bản gỗ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.55,Default,M,0,0,0,,{They were wood pieces \Nin all shapes and sizes,}Mấy miếng gỗ cỡ này,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but they all had their surface smoothed!}nhưng bề mặt lại nhẵn ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.50,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Oh, the firewood you brought home?}À, là đống gỗ con mang về hôm trước hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.08,Default,E,0,0,0,,{I used it, of course.}Mẹ dùng nó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.04,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You used it?}Mẹ dùng nó?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.02,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:33.42,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You can finally help with housework,}Cuối cùng con đã có thể giúp việc nhà,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:36.22,Default,E,0,0,0,,{and you tried so hard to \Nbring that firewood home.}và cố hết sức mang đống gỗ đó về.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:41.25,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I wanted to turn your \Nbedtime story into a book.}Con muốn lưu lại câu chuyện mẹ kể bằng nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.05,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's why I gathered those.}Nên đã làm ra đống gỗ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:46.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Oh, if you just want me to \Ntell you bedtime stories,}Nếu muốn nghe chuyện thế thì mẹ sẽ kể con nghe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,{I'd be glad to.}không phải ngại đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:52.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That's not... the point...}Vấn đề... không phải chỗ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.31,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Main?}Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.08,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What's happening?}Chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.66,Default,E,0,0,0,,{Main?}Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.08,Default,E,0,0,0,,Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.77,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I feel lik the fever's eating away at me.}Cảm giác cơn sốt đang ăn mòn mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:19.04,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I'm slowly fading away.}Mình đang dần biến mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.35,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.22,Default,M,0,0,0,,Lutz...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.19,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Main?}Cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.27,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I heard you collapsed suddenly.}Nghe nói cậu tự nhiên bất tỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.40,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Sorry to have worried you.}Xin lỗi vì làm cậu lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.24,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I'll go get your mom.}Tớ gọi dì lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.83,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It didn't work out again.}Lại thất bại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:49.51,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom burned... my wood tablets.}Mẹ... đã đốt hết bản gỗ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:54.58,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Ah... Well, they do look like pieces of wood.}À... thì nó trông giống gỗ thường mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:18:02.04,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I'm fated to never finish a book!}Tớ sẽ không thể nào làm sách được...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.91,Default,L,0,0,0,,{Don't beat yourself up.}Đừng có từ bỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.01,Default,M,0,0,0,,Lutz?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:15.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,{You just need to pick a material \Nthat doesn't burn, right?}Chỉ cần tìm nguyên liệu nào không bị cháy là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.69,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You're so nice, Lutz.}Cậu tốt bụng thật, Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:23.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,{I-I need you to introduce me to Mister Otto!}C-Chỉ là cảm ơn vì giới thiệu chú Otto với tớ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:27.35,Default,L,0,0,0,,{So you have to get better \Nno matter what. Got that?}Cậu phải khỏe lại đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.90,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Thanks, Lutz.}Ừm, cảm ơn Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.30,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{But even the bamboo strips \NLutz brought me...}Nhưng ngay cả những cây tre Lutz mang đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.44,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What was that noise?}Âm thanh gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.03,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Mom, what happened?}Mẹ, chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.95,Default,E,0,0,0,,{I thought Lutz brought us bamnicht wood,}Mẹ tưởng Lutz mang đến cho chúng ta gỗ Bamnicht,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.55,Default,E,0,0,0,,{but apparently not.}nhưng hóa ra không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.06,Default,M,0,0,0,,{You burned it?}Mẹ đốt sạch rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:57.06,Default,E,0,0,0,,{You don't need to worry. Just rest up.}Con không cần lo đâu, nghỉ ngơi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.82,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{The anger at something I made being burned,}Sự tức giận khi thứ mình tạo ra bị đốt cháy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.50,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{the frustration of that \Nanger not being understood,}sự thất vọng khi không ai hiểu về nó,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:17.32,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{the reality that no matter how many things \NI try, I can never have my books...}dù mình có thử bao nhiêu cách thì vẫn không thể tạo được sách...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I've had enough.}Đủ lắm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:24.63,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{If my efforts will never amount to anything,}Dù có cố gắng thế nào thì cũng chẳng có gì xảy ra,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:28.68,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{then I might as well disappear, right?}mình muốn biến mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:32.26,Flashback,F,0,0,0,,{Main.}Myne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.33,Flashback,F,0,0,0,,{Main!}Myne!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.77,Flashback,F,0,0,0,,{I'll help with whatever you want to do.}Tớ sẽ giúp cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.73,Flashback,F,0,0,0,,{I need you to introduce me to Mister Otto!}Tớ muốn cậu giới thiệu chú Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:45.61,Flashback,F,0,0,0,,{So you have to get better \Nno matter what. Got that?}Dù thế nào thì phải khỏe lại đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:49.37,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{That's right! I have to keep my promise!}Phải rồi, mình phải giữ lời hứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:53.08,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{I must get better and introduce him to Otto!}Mình phải khỏe lại và giới thiệu chú Otto cho cậu ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,{It's gone down.}Ủa? Nó biến mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:00.79,Default,M,0,0,0,,{The fever in my body is smaller now?}Cơn sốt đang hạ dần?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.87,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{There's something wrong with this fever.}Có gì đó kì lạ ở cơn sốt lần này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.28,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{It attacks me from the inside}Nó tấn công mình từ bên trong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.05,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{and keeps changing in size.}Và có thể thay đổi kích cỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:12.99,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What illness does this body have, anyway?}Cơ thể này đang mắc bệnh gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.69,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Are you all right now?}Cháu ổn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:21.13,Default,O,0,0,0,,{The captain told me that your fever \Ndidn't go down for five days.}Đội trưởng nói cháu sốt suốt 5 ngày không giảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but I'm fine.}Vâng, cháu vẫn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.53,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You look pale in the face.}Mặt cháu không ổn chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:32.26,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I've been racking my brain over something.}Cháu có một điều luôn lo nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.89,Default,M,0,0,0,,{I've tried all sorts of things \Nto make something I want,}Cháu đã thử mọi cách để tạo ra thứ mình muốn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.46,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but I just couldn't do it.}nhưng mãi không thể làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:42.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What would you do in my shoes?}Nếu là chú thì chú sẽ làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.08,Default,O,0,0,0,,{You can just hire someone to do it for you.}Chú sẽ thuê ai đó làm hộ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.34,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Hire someone myself?}Thuê ai đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.56,Default,M,0,0,0,,{That sounds like a great idea,}Cháu nghĩ đó là một ý tưởng,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.48,Default,M,0,0,0,,{but what if I don't have any capital?}nhưng nếu không có tiền thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:58.74,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Persuade someone who can do \Nit into doing it for you.}Thì thuyết phục ai đó có thể làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.82,Default,O,0,0,0,,{If it goes well, you don't \Nhurt your bottom line at all.}Nếu suôn sẻ thì cháu sẽ chẳng cần làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.78,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Once a businessman, always a businessman.}Không hổ danh là cựu thương nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.84,Default,M,0,0,0,,{But I'll keep that in mind.}Nhưng cháu sẽ tham khảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.50,Default,O,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}À phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.70,Default,O,0,0,0,,{About that meeting we had to postpone...}Về cuộc gặp bị hoãn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.31,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{And so, we decided on a suitable \Nday for Lutz and Otto to meet.}Và ngày chú Otto gặp Lutz đã được quyết định.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:21.32,Default,M,0,0,0,,{"Be at Central Plaza by the third bell."}"Gặp ở Đại lộ Trung Tâm, tiếng chuông thứ 3 vang lên"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.53,Default,O,0,0,0,,{He's a boy you're referring,}Là bạn của Myne giới thiệu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:27.37,Default,O,0,0,0,,{so I'm sure he'll be very amusing.}nên chú nghĩ thằng bé sẽ thú vị lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.60,Default,O,0,0,0,,{I'm looking forward to a fun day off.}Thật mong chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.95,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's that about?}Hả? Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.04,Italics,M,0,0,0,,{Isn't it gonna be just a meeting?}Chỉ là một cuộc gặp gỡ bình thường thôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:13.53,Next_Chapter,Title,0,0,0,,{Next Chapter\N}{\fs24}{Meeting}Chương sau: Cuộc gặp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:17.94,Default,M,0,0,0,,{High Priest, is there anything \Nspecial about the upcoming meeting?}Cha ơi, cuộc gặp đó có gì đặc biệt hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:21.58,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Why would I know anything \Nabout the affairs of commoners?}Tại sao lại hỏi ta vấn đề của thường dân?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:25.62,Default,M,0,0,0,,{Even you don't know, huh?}Cha không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:28.35,Default,F,0,0,0,,{Unlike you, I do have a good idea,}Không như con, ta có ý nghĩ trong đầu,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:30.55,Default,F,0,0,0,,{but I'm not going to jump to conclusions.}nhưng sẽ không nói ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:35.00,Default,M,0,0,0,,{What? Tell me if you have an idea!}Hả? Có gì thì nói ra đi chứ!
